HEADWORD: Sanitarian
<hw>San`i*ta"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to health, or the laws of health; sanitary.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sanitarian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Sanitarian
<hw>San`i*ta"ri*an</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An advocate of sanitary
measures; one especially interested or versed in sanitary
measures.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sanitarist</ent>⟦br⟧
